irectly, and the box will still not have `EXTENT_FINITE`.\r\n\r\nSee [this](https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2491/fix-2089-incorrect-model-visual-and/diff) gazebo pull request for an example of the issues this might cause.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>All boxes get <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/src/ac3e1c68e7ec682b6425d10ac62fd0c357fdbfed/include/ignition/math/BoxPrivate.hh?fileviewer=file-view-default#BoxPrivate.hh-41\" rel=\"nofollow\">initialized</a> with <code>EXTENT_NULL</code>. So it's possible that one sets the box minimum and maximum directly, and the box will still not have <code>EXTENT_FINITE</code>.</p>\n<p>See <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2491/fix-2089-incorrect-model-visual-and/diff\" rel=\"nofollow\">this</a> gazebo pull request for an example of the issues this might cause.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-11-08T16:49:39.466451+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-07-07T23:35:32.203202+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 53}